author: The Virginian-Pilot
title: Billiards | 9-ball Championships set for Oct. 25-30
text:
NORFOLK The 40th U.S. Open 9-Ball Championships will feature some of the top billiards players in the world later this month at the Sheraton Norfolk Waterside.
Play begins Oct. 25 with the final on Oct. 30.
General admission tickets are $10 per session. Information: 757-499-8900.
